node.text:
The highlight of 2020 for me was launching a business that marries my passion for medicine and beauty all rolled into one. That’s why I’m happy to announce that my brand @muze.labs will now be available at @musclelab. If you drop by the facility to workout or rehab, make sure to grab some wipes💧

It was important to find a brand that aligns with our mission to promote a healthy lifestyle for all people. Whether it’s skin care or fitness, it’s all about self care. Make this upcoming year about bettering yourself in all aspects. Muze does it all, because you do it all 🦾

node.text:
— Something’s coming & I’ve been anticipating this drop for a while. Most of you are new to my platform, but one thing that’s near & dear to my heart is my business baby @muze.labs 🖤

I launched this skin care brand with everything I had in me while IN pharmacy school and during a pandemic. Invested pretty much all I had, built the website myself when developers fell through, had an investor but decided to do it alone, had mentorship but no employees. The list goes on. 

BUT I did it because I wanted to create clean beauty products that I wish existed as a pharmacist. I travel, train, and I’m always on the go. I needed skin care that can keep up with my busy lifestyle! And I know a lot of you can relate.

Moral of the story? Keep following your dreams, no matter how challenging. Just make sure you come back and better. AND you can’t do it alone. Thank you to everyone that helped me with the relaunch. You are so appreciated. ✨

I achieve this with proper training, nutrition and supplementation. Head over to my link in bio and shop the number 1️⃣ supplements in the game! @1stphorm #IAM1STPHORM

— Happy Sunday! We out ladies and gentlemen ✈️ I’ve been working long and hard to bring to you a fun, exotic, once in a lifetime trip experience with me. Get your passports ready and let's go! 😍 

I've partnered with @onelovetravel.club to put together a 4-day content trip to Punta Cana, Dominican Republic. 🌴🇩🇴 This will be my first trip to DR, so we get to enjoy it together! Sign up NOW before we meet the max number of people!

We'll spend 4-days together capturing amazing content of course and while exploring DR with adventure activities like riding ATVs and chilling on a catamaran. ⚠️ Don’t forget to get your special DR. ROBIN B VIP EXCLUSIVE EXPERIENCE WITH ME by selecting “VIP UPGRADE” 🔝❤️ I can't wait to meet you guys! 

Head to http://onelovetravel.club/punta-cana-november-2021 to register. 

#Dr.RobinhitsDRwiththecrew
#OneLoveTakesDR #traveldoc #drrobinb

node.text:
— Never had to show off, just had to show up❗️I walked in my very first fashion show for my good sis & amazing designer @maxiejofficial x @ellaelisque ❤️ 

The energy was EVERYTHING! Thanks to everyone who snatched my look together. Yall left NO CRUMBS. ❌

Just a reminder — never allow people to put limits on what you’re capable of kings & queens. If you’re in the room, it’s because you belong there. Get comfortable being uncomfortable, that’s the only way you’ll grow. 📈

#drrobinb #prettylittledoctor #model #runway #fashionweek #ellaelisque

node.text:
— Look mama, it’s me on the big screen 🤩 If you needed a sign, here it is! BE THE BEST VERSION OF YOURSELF TODAY AND EVERY DAY 🦾

It’s not easy to push your body to new limits, but the GAINS are worth the temporary PAIN. 🔥

If you’re struggling to get energized in before the gym, try a pre-workout that’s right for you:

✨ Non-Stim: Endura-Formance & Alphasurge
✨ Mild-Stim: Megawatt
✨ High-Stim: Project-1

Mix & match your flavors using my link in bio under @1stphorm! There’s so much to choose from.

#fitness #drrobinb #1stphorm #iam1stphorm #thedoseshow #fitdoc
